n-earth-by-creating-hydrothermal-vents</guid></item><item><title>肠上皮 MHC II 类诱导脑炎 CD4 T 细胞并启动中枢神经系统自身免疫</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/intestinal-epithelial-mhc-class-ii-induces-encephalitogenic-cd4-t-cells-and-initiates-central-nervous-system-autoimmunity</link><description>科学。免疫学。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/intestinal-epithelial-mhc-class-ii-induces-encephalitogenic-cd4-t-cells-and-initiates-central-nervous-system-autoimmunity.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 12:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/intestinal-epithelial-mhc-class-ii-induces-encephalitogenic-cd4-t-cells-and-initiates-central-nervous-system-autoimmunity</guid></item><item><title>重新思考类脑人工智能：新研究揭示隐藏的不匹配</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/rethinking-brain-like-artificial-intelligence-new-study-reveals-hidden-mismatches</link><description>约克大学研究人员的一项新研究发现人工智能（AI）模型存在潜在的显着缺陷。人工神经网络 (ANN) 是一种为解决计算机视觉任务而构建的人工智能模型，令人惊讶地成为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rethinking-brain-like-artificial-intelligence-new-study-reveals-hidden-mismatches.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 11:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/rethinking-brain-like-artificial-intelligence-new-study-reveals-hidden-mismatches</guid></item><item><title>研究揭示了为什么某些癌症疗法并不适用于所有患者</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/study-reveals-why-some-cancer-therapies-dont-work-for-all-patients</link><description>阻断酪氨酸激酶酶的药物是最有效的癌症靶向疗法之一。然而，它们通常只对 40% 到 80% 预计对其有反应的患者有效。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/study-reveals-why-some-cancer-therapies-dont-work-for-all-patients2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 11:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/study-reveals-why-some-cancer-therapies-dont-work-for-all-patients</guid></item><item><title>人工智能从一份血液样本中识别出多种痴呆症</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-identifies-multiple-dementias-from-one-blood-sample</link><description>一次验血就能诊断痴呆症吗？研究人员利用人工智能和蛋白质组学从一份样本中识别出阿尔茨海默氏症、帕金森氏症和肌萎缩侧索硬化症。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-identifies-multiple-dementias-from-one-blood-sample.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 11:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-identifies-multiple-dementias-from-one-blood-sample</guid></item><item><title>使用合成电路控制电池比例</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cell-ratio-control-using-synthetic-circuits</link><description>PrimeC 的安全性与安慰剂相当，在 18 个月的治疗中，ALS 成人患者的功能衰退速度减缓，ALS 相关并发症减少，铁调节和 microRNA 生物标志物得到调节。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cell-ratio-control-using-synthetic-circuits2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 11:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/cell-ratio-control-using-synthetic-circuits</guid></item><item><title>与 II 级和 III 级胶质瘤死亡率和疾病进展相关的重要基因</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/significant-genes-associated-with-mortality-and-disease-progression-in-grade-ii-and-iii-glioma</link><description>背景：Wnt/β-catenin 通路在胶质瘤干细胞的肿瘤发生和维持中发挥着关键作用。本研究旨在利用癌症基因组图谱 (TCGA) 数据库评估与 II 级和 III 级神经胶质瘤患者死亡率和疾病进展相关的 Wnt/β-catenin 通路相关的重要基因。方法：我们从 TCGA 数据库中获取了 515 例 II 级和 III 级胶质瘤患者的临床病理信息和 mRNA 表达数据。我们进行了多变量 Cox 回归分析，以确定与神经胶质瘤预后独立相关的基因。结果：对参与 Wnt/β-catenin 信号传导的 34 个基因的分析表明，与 Wnt/β-catenin 通路相关的 4 个基因（CER1、FRAT1、FSTL1 和 RPSA）与 II 级和 III 级胶质瘤患者的死亡率和疾病进展显着相关。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/significant-genes-associated-with-mortality-and-disease-progression-in-grade-ii-and-iii-glioma2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 10:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/significant-genes-associated-with-mortality-and-disease-progression-in-grade-ii-and-iii-glioma</guid></item><item><title>独立工作室联合创始人认为，“没有人关心”巨大的开放世界，相反，开发者应该只选择一件事，并将其做得“非常好”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/indie-studio-co-founder-believes-nobody-cares-about-huge-open-worlds-anymore-instead-devs-should-pick-just-one-thing-and-do-it-exceptionally-well</link><description>我确实感受到了大型游戏的倦怠。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/indie-studio-co-founder-believes-nobody-cares-about-huge-open-worlds-anymore-instead-devs-should-pick-just-one-thing-and-do-it-exceptionally-well.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 10:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/indie-studio-co-founder-believes-nobody-cares-about-huge-open-worlds-anymore-instead-devs-should-pick-just-one-thing-and-do-it-exceptionally-well</guid></item></channel></rss>